quran[4{c,v,t}:
6,143,"yeh aath nar o madah hain, do bheer ki qisam se aur do bakri ki qisam se, ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! un se pucho ke Allah ne unn ke nar haraam kiye hain ya madah, ya woh bachay jo bheiron aur bakrion ke pait mein hon? theek theek ilm ke sath mujhe batao agar tum sachey ho"
6,144,"aur isi terhan do oont ki qisam se hain aur do gaaye ki qisam se pucho, inn ke nar Allah ne haraam kiye hain ya madah, ya woh bachay jo oontni aur gaaye ke pait mein hon? kya tum uss waqt haazir thay jab Allah ne un ke haraam honay ka hukum tumhe diya tha? phir uss shakhs se barh kar zalim aur kon hoga jo Allah ki taraf mansoob kar ke jhooti baat kahe taakay ilm ke baghair logon ki ghalat raah namai kere yaqeenan Allah aisay zaalmon ko raah raast nahi dekhata"
6,145,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! un se kaho ke jo wahi tumahray paas aayi hai is mein to mein koi cheez aisi nahi paata jo kisi khanay walay par haraam ho, ila yeh ke woh Murdaar ho, ya bahaya howa khoon ho, ya suar ka gosht ho ke woh napak hai, ya fisq ho ke Allah ke siwa kisi aur ke naam par zibah kya gaya ho phir jo shakhs majaboori ki haalat mein ( koi cheez inn mein se kha le ) baghair is ke ke woh nafarmani ka iradah rakhta ho aur baghair is ke ke woh hadd zaroorat se tajawaz kere, to yaqeenan tumhara rab Dur guzar se kaam lainay wala aur reham frmane wala hai"
6,146,"aur jin logon ne yahoodiyat ikhtiyar ki un par hum ne sab naakhun walay janwar haraam kar diye thay, aur gaaye aur bakri ki charbi bhi bajuz uss ke jo unn ki peeth ya unn ki anton se lagi hui ho ya haddi se lagi reh jaye yeh hum ne un ki sar kashi ki saza unhen di thi aur yeh jo kuch hum keh rahay hain bilkul sach keh rahay hain"
